public class Orkut
extends GoogleClient

Service definition for Orkut (v2).

Lets you manage activities, comments and badges in Orkut. More stuff coming in time.

For more information about this service, see the API Documentation

This service uses JsonHttpRequestInitializer to initialize global parameters via its Orkut.Builder. Sample usage: 

  public class OrkutRequestInitializer implements JsonHttpRequestInitializer {
      public void initialize(JsonHttpRequest request) {
        OrkutRequest orkutRequest = (OrkutRequest)request;
        orkutRequest.setPrettyPrint(true);
        orkutRequest.setKey(ClientCredentials.KEY);
    }
  }

Since:
1.3.0
